n|-\n|1993\n|''Survive the Night''\n|Stacy\n|TV film\n|-\n|1993\n|''[[Poisoned by Love: The Kern County Murders]]''\n|Edie Ballew\n|TV film\n|-\n|1993\n|''Trial & Error''\n|Katherine Woodfield\n|TV film\n|-\n|1994\n|''{{sortname|The|Forget-Me-Not Murders|nolink=1}}''\n|Monique\n|TV film\n|-\n|1994\n|''Ride with the Wind''\n|Katherine Barnes\n|TV film\n|-\n|1994\n|''[[Without Consent]]''\n|Nora Fields\n|TV film\n|-\n|1994\n|''Janek: The Silent Betrayal''\n|Monique Dessier\n|TV film\n|-\n|1995\n|''Falling for You''\n|Mary\n|TV film\n|-\n|1995\n|''{{sortname|The|Outer Limits|The Outer Limits (1995 TV series)}}''\n|Cathy Kress\n|\"[[The Sandkings]]\"\n|-\n|1996-99\n|''[[Poltergeist: The Legacy]]''\n|Dr. Rachel Corrigan\n|Main role\n|-\n|1997\n|''[[Dead Man's Gun]]''\n|Dianna McKinney\n|\"Next of Kin\"\n|-\n|1998\n|''{{sortname|The|Sweetest Gift|nolink=1}}''\n|Mrs. Martin\n|TV film\n|-\n|1999\n|''{{sortname|The|First Gentleman|nolink=1}}''\n|Marjorie Litchfield\n|TV Film\n|-\n|2000\n|''[[Common Ground (2000 film)|Common Ground]]''\n|Janet\n|TV film\n|-\n|2001-02\n|''{{sortname|The|Education of Max Bickford}}''\n|Erica Bettis\n|Main role\n|-\n|2003\n|''{{sortname|The|Risen|nolink=1}}''\n|Lynn Todd\n|TV film\n|-\n|2003\n|''[[D.C. Sniper: 23 Days of Fear]]''\n|Sandy Moose\n|TV film\n|-\n|2004\n|''{{sortname|The|L Word}}''\n|Faye Buckley\n|\"Luck, Next Time\", \"Liberally\"\n|-\n|2004\n|''{{sortname|The|4400}}''\n|Barbara Yates\n|\"Becoming\", \"Trial by Fire\"\n|-\n|2008\n|''{{sortname|A|Very Merry Daughter of the Bride}}''\n|Rose\n|TV film\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20070929102811/http://www.filmreferencelibrary.ca/index.asp?layid=46&csid1=786&navid=87 Canadian Film Encyclopedia: A publication of The Film Reference Library/a division of the Toronto International Film Festival Group]\n*{{IMDb name|0001726}}\n*{{Twitter}}\n\n{{ACCT Best Actress}}\n{{ACCT Best Supporting Actress}}\n{{Authority 